@notifBase = http://localhost:8002/api/v1
@internalToken = internal_secret_token

### Emitir evento — notificación de chat a múltiples usuarios
POST {{notifBase}}/internal/events/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

{
  "event_type": "chat.member.invited",
  "recipient_ids": [10, 20, 30],
  "actor_id": 5,
  "actor_name": "admin.user",
  "context": {"chat_id": 99, "chat_name": "Equipo de diseño"}
}


### Emitir evento — email de seguridad (con recipient_email para evitar round-trip al auth service)
POST {{notifBase}}/internal/events/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

{
  "event_type": "auth.password.changed",
  "recipient_ids": [42],
  "context": {
    "recipient_email": "usuario@ejemplo.com",
    "recipient_name": "Usuario Ejemplo"
  }
}


### Emitir evento — anuncio administrativo
POST {{notifBase}}/internal/events/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

{
  "event_type": "admin.broadcast",
  "recipient_ids": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
  "actor_name": "Equipo Aura",
  "context": {"message": "Mantenimiento programado el viernes a las 22:00 hs."}
}
